{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a half a day, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Jewish agency paid for us, paid the kibbutz whatever medical expenses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after, after being in the kibbutz for a little while, they, they examined my feet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they decided to do some surgery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they brought me to a beautiful hospital in Haifa on the Carmel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they did-- they removed certain sections in my foot to make it possible for the skin to grow, sort of closer to each other, and-- because there was a lot of scar tissue.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and they provided me with orthopedic shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my life was, was improved considerably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since, since I could speak Hebrew, and I was a little older than the rest of them, so I was put in a position of management of the group.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sort of their leader for a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the presentations and knowing the language, sort of put me in a position of leadership.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we, we were approximately 40 children that we came to the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some single kids were added on to us from various-- the Jewish agency used to evaluate, when a single child appeared from some location or he lived with older people, they attached him to us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- in the kibbutz, we were trained to go and make our own settlements.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The purpose of our being in the kibbutz, they called this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a preparatory step for, for creating our own settlement at some location, which was strategically important.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So each one of us was assigned jobs in various areas of the kibbutz, so we would have total knowledge how to run the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
